100],"##{101}":[101,101],"##{102}":[102,103],"#1268 Refactoring: Forgeron-Pfade aus imports.js entfernt, Importe in Komponenten verlagert.":[128,128],"#1270 Bug: Letztes Bild in MediaCollection kann nicht entfernt werden. New Media":[129,129],"#1212 Feature: `useForgeron()` Composable einführen; temporäre Daten über `ResourceRequest` verwalten.":[130,130],"#1278 Feature: Zeichenlimit 'Firma' (Adresse) auf 60 erhöht; Validierung & Zähler-UI angepasst.":[131,132],"#1278 Feature: Zeichenlimit 'Firma' (Adresse) auf 60 erhöht; Validierung & Zähler-UI angepasst.#{1}":[132,132],"#1290 Task: Barrierefreiheit im Frontend prüfen & unerfüllte Anforderungen für Folgetickets listen.":[133,133],"#1313 Refactor monolithic checkout component into smaller, single-responsibility child components for improved maintainability and performance.":[134,134],"#1316 Implement **separate navigation caches** for different admin areas (e.g., shop admin, customer admin) to prevent display issues when switching tabs.":[135,135],"#1325 Reintroduce missing address fields to the updated address UI to prevent data loss and ensure complete address and contact information capture.":[136,136],"#1328 Fix: Toggle-Buttons in Admin-Einstellungsgruppen sind jetzt funktionsfähig.":[137,137],"#888 Anpassung PDP für Kombiprodukte: Prinect-Status ausblenden, alle Bestandteile anzeigen.":[138,138],"#1333 Refactored PrintDataActions.vue into child components to reduce complexity and improve maintainability.":[139,139],"#1014 Checked and implemented Microsoft Advertising's consent mode for UET tags to meet privacy requirements.":[140,140],"#1341 Hid the dark mode toggle icon for all user roles except Techadmin and Admin.":[141,141],"#888 Adjusted combo product PDP: Removed 'Prinect-Status' column and now list all components, restricting view icons by user permissions.":[142,142],"#1237 Fixed shipping date selection: disabled unavailable dates, corrected cost display for \"on request\" shipping, and fixed validation errors.":[143,143],"#1296 Applied frontend address validation rules (character limits, required fields) to the admin area for consistency.":[144,144],"#1342 Replaced the MIME type with the correct file extension (e.g., jpg, pdf) in the downloads display.":[145,145],"#1305:Refactored the admin area to the new Forgeron structure, moving CSS/JS into a package and finalizing the new admin skin.":[146,147],"#1305:Refactored the admin area to the new Forgeron structure, moving CSS/JS into a package and finalizing the new admin skin.#{1}":[147,147],"#1365 Refactored address validation to use a single, centralized source for both frontend and backend rules to remove code duplication.":[148,148],"#780 Fixed the \"items per page\" selector and pagination, corrected the product count display, and unified the component's font.":[149,149],"#1377 : Improved the PDP layout for product properties: dropdowns are now larger, have closer labels, and an updated, more intuitive style.":[150,150],"#1376 Split the approvals area into \"Pending\" and \"Processed\" tabs to provide a clearer overview and separate open from completed tasks.":[151,151],"#1331 Fixed a bug where a new address created in the cart was not automatically selected; the new address is now set as active.":[152,153],"#1331 Fixed a bug where a new address created in the cart was not automatically selected; the new address is now set as active.#{1}":[153,153],"#1381 Re-enabled shipping and billing address selection, including a search function, in the checkout process within the MEO-Shop-Skin. And some other bugs":[154,155],"#1381 Re-enabled shipping and billing address selection, including a search function, in the checkout process within the MEO-Shop-Skin. And some other bugs###Contributions for **Sep 24, 2025**":[155,155]},"outlinks":[],"task_lines":[]},
